data.description: Come check out this gem located in McAllen's highly sought after Vendome subdivision! House has tons of space and remarkable finishes throughout! This beauty features stucco on block, foam insulation, quartz countertops, double door entry with 8 ft interior doors, high ceilings, custom remote controlled blinds in the living room and master bedroom, custom cabinets, an extended 2 car garage, fence around the entire home and is equipped with a sprinkler system!! NOT TO MENTION ALL APPLIANCES ARE CONVEYING WITH THE SELL OF THE HOME!!! With 4 bedrooms and 3 FULL baths, there is plenty of space for the entire family to experience modern living at its finest. Walk through the back doors where you'll find a covered patio with a very spacious backyard. What doesn't this place have!! This home has massive curb appeal and the subdivision is on fire! Come check this place out, it won't last.
